justin2hale:
I have another solution for this.
create a projects folder as a sister folder to your main sass folder:
-sass/
--style.scss
-projects/
--project1/
---style.scss
---koala.config.json
In your project1 style.scss:
@import "../../sass/style";
In the koala.config.json file:
{
     "mappings": [ 
          {
               "src": "",
               "dest": "output/to/your/project/"
          }
     ],
...
}
Recreate this process as many times as you need for each project that you want to share the same output.
.

